summary: Are you ready to try a new experience? This is a saved file at level 1 in Riverwood.. I call her Saphire. She is a creation of the Succubus Race
descriptionHtml:
Are you ready to try a new experience? This is a saved file at level 1 in Riverwood.. I call her Saphire.

I haven't spent much time playing this character.. yet, But with the special powers and spells that she has, I know that it is going to be fun.


She is a creation of the Succubus Race - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22903

This mod requires ApachiiHair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168


The outfits in the screen shots can be found here:

Gatti 14 Yumiko Suits for CBBEv3 - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19257
Dark Lilith Sexy Succubus Armor - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13067

Other mods that I use, may play a part in this character:

Caliente's BBE Body Mod - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666
The Eyes Of Beauty - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13722
Hair packs of TES IV Oblivion - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18110
